    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good summary, but i feel like some of those \"against\" points aren't really backed by data as much as the benefits are. like, is there actually any solid evidence that immigration causes wage suppression, or is that just a common talking point? i've read that most studies show it's pretty negligible.",
